{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up, lost in an unfamiliar place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Aim far away...&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A voice echoes in your head.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Just get far away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you go far away from your base, enemies will appear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The weather changes every time you die and return to your base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The enemies that appear will change depending on the weather.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you defeat an enemy, they will occasionally drop materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The materials dropped by each type of enemy will also vary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hint: You can use the materials dropped by stone golems that appear on sunny days to make your first craft, and then place various things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place an alchemy desk and fields to improve crops and grow vegetables.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eat the items you've grown to improve your abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can expect to improve various abilities by improving crops.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739368301","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/page.bg.jpg?t=1739368301","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/f2882993c262d16b748247cc9b0534ef06ac07ba/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739368301","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/f2882993c262d16b748247cc9b0534ef06ac07ba/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739368301","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p cl